      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Which towns in the Sebago Lakes Region have dispensaries?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Currently: Windham (Route 302 'Green Mile' cluster), Casco (Route 302 Roosevelt Trail), Bridgton (Portland Road corridor), Raymond (Roosevelt Trail), and Standish (Northeast Road). Towns without dispensaries include Naples, Sebago, Harrison, Fryeburg, Lovell, Denmark, and Brownfield — all of which represent delivery service opportunities."
      }
